ygData.messageBody:
Welcome to the Warrior emailing list. This is a small rapidly growing
list and promises to be the best source of information for Everquest
Warriors on the net. Tell your friends, post information on the message
boards, get the word out. To subscribe people need to go to www.onelist.com
and subscribe to the warriors_eq mailing list or go directly to
www.onelist.com/subscribe/warriors_eq Email can be sent to the emailing
list at warriors_eq@onelist.com

Recommend registering for the digest not the regular email version. The
digests are mailed out once or twice a day and wont flood your mailbox the
way regular email can.

For the Honor and Glory of Rellos Zek;

Patty of Halas
